dog trial
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a competition to select the most skilful sheepog-and-handler combinations by means of set problems in sheep control.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
